    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We monitored the transmissibility of 2019 novel coronavirus disease in Zhejiang accounting the transmissions from imported cases. Even though Zhejiang is one of the worst-affected provinces, an interruption of disease transmission (i.e. instantaneous reproduction numbers &lt;1) was observed in early/mid-February after an early social-distancing response to the outbreak.</jats:p>",
